A small app to count the points for a contest about the FIFA World Cup in Brazil.
Each participant choses 8 Teams and get points eveytime they win a game.
Teams don't have the same weight.

1 point/win     2 points/win    3 points/win    5 points/win    7 points/win
Spain           Italy           Russia          Costa Rica      Japan
Germany         Greece          Mexico          Iran            Cameroon
Portugal        England         Croatia         Ghana           Korea Republic
Brazil          Belgium         Ivory Coast     Nigeria         Australia
Colombia        Chile           Bosnia-Herz     
Uruguay         USA             Algeria     
Argentina       Netherlands     Ecuador     
Switzerland     France          Honduras        

Points are stored in a SQLite DB and results are accessible via a minimalist website
